                    "value": "<p>The drude targets a creature they can see within 30 feet and assaults it with illusions of ghosts and nightly terrors. The creature must attempt a @Check[will|dc:18] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected and temporarily immune for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes @Damage[1d6[mental]] damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes @Damage[1d6[mental]] damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes @Damage[2d6[mental]] damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>"
